    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable surface scratches, some minor door dings, and light paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some minor staining consistent with regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. It is a dependable workhorse that has been maintained to ensure safety and functionality, making it a great value for those prioritizing utility over cosmetics.",
