    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this fantastic project opportunity! While this vehicle is currently in poor condition and will need some serious TLC to get back on the road, it\u2019s the perfect blank canvas for a restoration enthusiast or someone looking for a rewarding mechanical challenge. It's an affordable way to start your next big automotive adventure!",
