    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. The exterior is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Every component, from the engine to the electronic systems, functions perfectly, and it has been meticulously maintained with a documented service history. A buyer can expect a car that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line, requiring no immediate maintenance or cosmetic repairs.",
      "price": 49800.0,
