    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and it has been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-loved. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go. I've priced it to sell quickly, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain delivers linear power through a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded Bilstein dampers for improved lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals\u2014including oil pressure and compression\u2014remain within factory tolerances. This is an excellent opportunity to own a high-performance icon optimized for the enthusiast who values powertrain precision and mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Reliable used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance completed. Clean title. Functional interior and exterior.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
